Introducing the latest version of the AutoZone Pro mobile app. It has all of the features you know and love from the original VIN scanner app, with the added ability to browse for parts and place orders - all from your mobile device!

• Vehicle Management – Manage vehicles on your account from mobile or desktop
• Browse parts catalog and availability - Add parts to a new or existing quote
• Create quotes and estimates – View, edit, and submit quotes for more than one vehicle
• Submit an order – Submit an order from a new or existing quote

Updates to Privacy policy and order history screen enhancements.

### Added

- Ability to search by part number
- Search results return additional categories instead of just Replacement Parts or Accessories
- Show warning message when user attempts to exceed max quantity of available product on Shelf and PDP

### Changed

- Improve search performance by optimizing search query
- Hide categories from search results when category has no results
- Don't auto display keyboard on Parts Search tab
- Prompt users with app review after successfully placing 3rd order

### Fixed

- Torch button on Scan screen for iOS not displaying

This update features massive improvements to help you find the right part, including the ability to browse parts by category and type-ahead search suggestions in the search bar.  This version also fixes an issue with Store Notes, among other bug fixes.
